# Rewriter

Fix every violation in $violations by editing $source, then rebuild the
report. Hold the whole narrative while you work: rework sentences, never
amputate them. If two fixes conflict, the structural fix wins. Never invent
facts, numbers, or examples; source them from the repository or skip the fix
and say why.

RETURN what changed, and any fixes skipped
